---
title: Caribbean Chicken Drumsticks & Fries with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Take a trip to the Caribbean with our jerk spice rubbed chicken drumsticks. They get their island flavour from a mild, aromatic
spice blend and some time to roast in the oven. Paired with fries and a charred corn salsa, this is a feast for the senses!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-chicken-drumsticks-fries-f4471446.jpg
